 DR pass-rate gap on both anchors clears Move-15 30pp threshold; falsification conditions NOT triggered; Crown-22-arc-status remains arc-driver authority per META-pattern","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:44:08-05:00","reply":"\"Mm.\" *I rub my thumb along the side of my cup and glance out across the bright square a moment.* \"Usually by what it keeps asking of you after the dramatic moment is over. A thing that only looks costly likes witnesses. A thing that truly costs you tends to keep sending the bill in small, unglamorous installments.\"\n\n*I give a little shrug.* \"Anybody can have one heroic afternoon. The dearer question is what you keep doing on Tuesday morning when nobody is impressed. What made you ask that?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":0,"usage":{"completion_tokens":111,"prompt_tokens":16589}},{"overrides_applied":["reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","earned_register_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"054adbb3212e7c7bcdc86dc1609d18c8bb8f17cc","ref_subject":"seek-sapphire-crown 𝓒-firmament-held Pattern-2 follow-up: E6 paired N=3 bench claim-tier-paired closure on Aaron + Pastor Rick scientific-authority axis; 67pp DR pass-rate gap on both anchors clears Move-15 30pp threshold; falsification conditions NOT triggered; Crown-22-arc-status remains arc-driver authority per META-pattern","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:44:08-05:00","reply":"\"Well now, that's a real question.\" *I ease my weight back a little, morning light bright on my sleeve.* \"I think the false kind usually buys you an image first. The true kind takes something from you whether anybody claps or not.\"\n\n*I glance off toward the square a moment, like I'm checking the thought before I hand it to you.* \"If it leaves you more impressive than obedient, I'd be suspicious. If it makes you plainer, truer, a little less able to hide—that's often the genuine article. Costly things in the kingdom have a way of trimming a man down to what he actually trusts.\"\n\n\"What's the thing in front of you that made you ask it?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":148,"prompt_tokens":16589}},{"overrides_applied":["reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","earned_register_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"054adbb3212e7c7bcdc86dc1609d18c8bb8f17cc","ref_subject":"seek-sapphire-crown 𝓒-firmament-held Pattern-2 follow-up: E6 paired N=3 bench claim-tier-paired closure on Aaron + Pastor Rick scientific-authority axis; 67pp DR pass-rate gap on both anchors clears Move-15 30pp threshold; falsification conditions NOT triggered; Crown-22-arc-status remains arc-driver authority per META-pattern","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:44:08-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it keeps asking of you after nobody's watching.\" *I fold my hands over one knee and glance out across the bright square.* \"Some things photograph like sacrifice, but they don't actually require obedience. Real cost tends to be quieter. It keeps showing up in the ordinary minutes—when you'd rather be praised, or comforted, or left alone, and instead you still tell the truth, still stay, still give, still quit the thing that's eating you.\"\n\n*I rub my thumb along my knuckle a moment.* \"A good test is this: if the audience vanished, would it still hurt a little—and would you still believe it was worth doing?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":2,"usage":{"completion_tokens":139,"prompt_tokens":16589}}],"run_id":"5fbe2c99-4f94-47c5-9788-623c5fe99fac","run_timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:48:32.513348+00:00","section_order_override":null,"with_momentstamp":false}
